==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unknit
<hw>Un*knit"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>knit</ets>.]</ety> <def>To undo or unravel what is
knitted together.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Fie, fie! <qex>unknit</qex> that threatening unkind brow.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unknot</ent>⟦br⟧
